data.description: Precious bungalow conveniently located close to USA Hospital, downtown Mobile, Midtown restaurants, and parks. This charming home has beautiful hardwood floors, arched doorways, and new flooring in the kitchen. There are 2 bedrooms and a full bath downstairs and 2 bedrooms, a full bath, and a sun room upstairs. Other rooms include a formal living room, dining room, breakfast room. Large fenced backyard and deck for entertaining. Listing Company makes no representation as to accuracy of square footage :buyer to verify.
